{"tid":1520150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正苦有劇本，我地都有主線劇本：九月春袋祭、十月国慶匯演","createTime":"2019-08-30T17:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:27:00.000Z","uid":90601,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64ce3b188cb3e430e5cfe0d92157c66cf9ec8632","tid":1520150,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:09:42.000Z","msg":"大家都知道，香港人無槍無炮，無人可以一時三刻解決正苦同中央<br />\n唯一可以做既，好老土，就係鬥長命，不斷令正苦犯錯，不斷削弱佢地既威信<br />\n所以一定要長遠之計去考慮<br />\n要記得，我地自己都有劇本！<br />\n<br />\n聽日831，只係劇本既一部分<br />\n代表香港人不畏政府高壓反對，自發無大台既自由行<br />\n勇和結合，橫掃港島，然後(理想上)不被補不流血<br />\n<br />\n跟住落黎既劇本<br />\n就係九月「機場春袋祭」<br />\n每個禮拜同和你飛、和你塞<br />\n直擊正苦經濟命脈<br />\n<br />\n然後，就係十月一，国慶互放煙花大匯演<br />\n依個先係短期劇本既重頭戲<br />\n會做咩，相信大家一個月後會有明確答案<br />\n<br />\n再落黎，就甚至係施政報告，11月區選，重推明日大愚等各種惡法<br />\n我地要用正苦鬥長命，適時重擊，然後待命，令正苦坐立不安，打唔響賣港算盤<br />\n依個就係我地既劇本<br />\n要鬥長命，做足劇本，就要不被捕不流血，仲要唔好中途offine<br />\n<br />\n今日發生左好多事，相信黎緊九月會更凶險<br />\n大家唔可以自亂陣腳，貿然冒進<br />\n對家有無劇本都好，我地只要跟足自己既劇本，就已經夠<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安 光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2467780d8b4bedfbdfd340e675dcc05e2d55636c","tid":1520150,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=e5d3ed1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=8cd3b8b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=7bd35573\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"db6b42e27f5d8c286481d8da6ea136b1a7986dae","tid":1520150,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"１／１０"},{"pid":"0600afdc83fdf85a2ab286d41cc75d894fda874e","tid":1520150,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"咩最後一戰呀？明明就係無限之戰，你對手係赤納粹，有二三十年要捱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519888</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f028830279d93d7813914876c0ffacecd9ba9449","tid":1520150,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUpTHxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUpTHxB.jpg&h=6bd49a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n點解政府做咁多嘢煲大民怨<br />\n急住要喺831決戰<br />\n因為九月有機場有三罷<br />\n記住不受傷不被捕<br />\n九月份繼續齊上齊落<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ea0a06f153c00961889c462e122a94cd9c054401","tid":1520150,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"２／１０"},{"pid":"4cca73896d80d1bac77aa248a054e539c67c43f4","tid":1520150,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:10:44.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f18ac421c8ce970d419e9df3f4f91993da7511","tid":1520150,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"３／１０"},{"pid":"bf9cd548359c8cd55024deabe8ea25e462bafca3","tid":1520150,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl